data.title: Vietnam on the Mic
data.meta_description: Listen to Vietnam on the Mic on Spotify. Listen as Justine Mach interviews the youth of Vietnam! From conversations about food and school to cultural differences as the country develops, Vietnam on the Mic showcases all aspects of what Generation Z is up to in Vietnam. Regardless of whether you are a Vietnamese living abroad, an international student trying to connect with the local culture, or simply a parent trying to understand your children, join in weekly to hear from our wonderful guest speakers!
